          &lt;a href=&#34;[https://en.cppreference.com/w/cpp/language/usual_arithmetic_conversions](https://en.cppreference.com/w/cpp/language/usual_arithmetic_conversions)&#34; class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;cppreference：usual arithmetic conversions&lt;/a&gt;
          &lt;p class=&#34;desc&#34;&gt;混合整型运算时的提升与转换规则&lt;/p&gt;
